DEPENDS:
1. clx
2. bordeaux-threads
3. log5

INSTALL METHODS:

Add the following code to your .stumpwmrc file,
;; Load stumpwm tray.
(load "~/Source/stumpwm-tray/stumptray.lisp")
;; Define the two command to control tray create and destroy.
(defcommand create-tray () ()
  (simpletray:create))
(defcommand destroy-tray () ()
  (simpletray:destroy))


